  "title": "A flashing white UFO spotted in Taguatinga-DF [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/28/a-flashing-white-ufo-spotted-in-taguatinga-df-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1ag",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>APRIL 3rd, 1996</strong>. Time: 21h00. Duration: 1 minute. In the region of Taguatinga, Distrito Federal, a person observed an unidentified flying object in the shape of a &#8220;white flashing light&#8221;. The UFO was seen when the observer looked at Southern Cross with the naked eye and on a &#8220;clear sky&#8221; night. According to the witness, the UFO had an &#8220;airplane&#8221; speed and was moving vertically, &#8220;only rising&#8221;. The witness was unable to estimate the altitude of the unknown object. No photographs or footage of the sighting were taken.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.435. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Taguatinga, Distrito Federal”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
